step 1) make your html file and link it css file from link tag
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

step 2) go to website name unplash choose your intersted images type for example (computer) or you can choose random
https://unsplash.com/

step 3) after selecting 
make body tag and paste that link in it at set background with background property
body {
  background-image: url("https://source.unsplash.com/random/1920x1080"); /* Background image */
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  height: 100vh; /* Ensure full viewport height */
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center; /* Center horizontally */
  align-items: center; /* Center vertically */
}
here it is
